data.name: ReadDisbSuppressionStatusHistoryCollectionType
data.value: select top(1) CPA_TYPE, CSP_NUMBER, DSS_GENERATED_ID, CLT_SEQUENTIAL_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, TYPE from CKT_DISB_SUPPR_STS where (TYPE = @type) and (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE > @effectiveDate) and (CPA_TYPE = 'E') and (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (CLT_SEQUENTIAL_ID = @cltSequentialId)
